title: Grateful Dead Live at San Diego Sports Arena on 1973-11-14
lineage: Transfer of re-shelled master cassettes on November 12, 2023 using a Nakamichi CR-7A > Tascam DA-3000 @ 24 bit 96 kHz
taper: Recorded by Charles Conner from center right
description:
Set I
Big Railroad Blues
Jack Straw
Sugaree
Mexicali Blues
Here Comes Sunshine
Black Throated Wind
Cumberland Blues
Row Jimmy
The Race Is On
Brown Eyed Women
Beat It On Down The Line
Tennessee Jed
El Paso
China Cat Sunflower >
I Know You Rider
Around & Around
Set II
Truckin' >
The Other One >
Big River >
The Other One >
Eyes Of The World >
The Other One >
Wharf Rat
Me & My Uncle
Goin' Down The Road Feeling Bad >
One More Saturday Night
 
Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Keith Godchaux - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Donna Jean Godchaux - Vocals
